---
layout: layouts/base.njk
title: 探索
description: 读书、思考与随手试验
---

<section class="section">
  <h2 class="section-title">探索</h2>
  <p class="card-desc">这里更偏“输入与灵感”：读书、作品、随手实验与观点备忘，保留未经打磨但有价值的第一手笔记。</p>
  <div class="card-grid">
    {% for note in collections.explorationsList %}
      <article class="card">
        <a class="card-link" href="{{ note.url }}">
          <h3 class="card-title">{{ note.data.title }}</h3>
          {% if note.data.description %}
            <p class="card-desc">{{ note.data.description }}</p>
          {% endif %}
        </a>
      </article>
    {% endfor %}
  </div>
</section>
